She was thankful for the change in subject. Her logic circiuts and her vocal 
wiring were not working straight all of a sudden. She went over to the table 
and started working on the equipment that Scorponok had told her to work on. 
  In the middle of fixing one of his tables, she walked over to him and 
whispered into his ear, "I like you a lot too commander. Sorry for being 
such an idiot earlier.  By vocal circuits got tied up.  But your not so bad 
looking yourself commander."
She smiled at him the reflected the warmth in her spark for him.  Then she 
turned back to the table and finished working on the hydrolics on it.
